description: dlt is an open-source python-first scalable data loading library that does not require any backend to run.
name: dlt

dependencies.name: psycopg2cffi
dependencies.kind: platform_python_implementation == "PyPy" and (extra == "postgres" or extra == "redshift" or extra == "postgis")

dependencies.name: pyarrow
dependencies.kind: extra == "bigquery" or extra == "parquet" or extra == "motherduck" or extra == "athena" or extra == "synapse" or extra == "clickhouse" or extra == "dremio" or extra == "lancedb" or extra == "deltalake" or extra == "pyiceberg"

dependencies.name: s3fs
dependencies.kind: extra == "filesystem" or extra == "s3" or extra == "athena" or extra == "clickhouse"

dependencies.name: gcsfs
dependencies.kind: extra == "gcp" or extra == "bigquery" or extra == "gs" or extra == "clickhouse"
